text: "Thick of It" is a song by KSI. It was his No.1 in December 2024. It became very popular after people made fun of how "mid" the song was. It was released on 3 October 2024. The album was called Thick of It(Chorus). The song featured Trippie Redd which helped him compose the song. == Popularity from TikTok and YouTube == "Thick Of It" has gotten popularity from TikTok and YouTube mainly from the song being called "mid". That is a term used by Gen Z and Gen Alpha to refer to something thats in the middle basically its middle but shorten.
